        <p id="Par48">The theorem follows from Lemma <xref ref-type="sec" rid="FPar3">3</xref> and the fact that every cycle <italic>C</italic> in <italic>G</italic> can be written as an <inline-formula id="IEq221"><alternatives><tex-math id="M441">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
