        <p>Thm. <xref ref-type="sec" rid="FPar5">4</xref> suggests the following, conservative heuristic to extract an orientable subgraph from <italic>G</italic>: <def-list><def-item><term>(1)</term><def><p id="Par50">Construct a maximum weight spanning tree <inline-formula id="IEq226"><alternatives><tex-math id="M451">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
