        <p>It follows that the heuristic to extract an orientable subgraph can be implemented in linear time: <def-list><def-item><term>(1)</term><def><p id="Par64">An <inline-formula id="IEq291"><alternatives><tex-math id="M581">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
