<inline-graphic xlink:href="13015_2021_186_Figd_HTML.gif" id="d32e9662"/> are sorted contiguously, i.e., a new path is initiated only after the previous one cannot be continued any further. Note that keeping track of the total input weight from <italic>W</italic> does not alter the <inline-formula id="IEq336"><alternatives><tex-math id="M655">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
