        <p id="Par77">Our modified Kahn algorithm keeps the not-yet-sorted vertices in a priority queue instead of a simple queue. The priority of a vertex <inline-formula id="IEq359"><alternatives><tex-math id="M695">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
