    <sec id="Sec12">
      <title>Consensus sequence</title>
      <p id="Par107">The final step is the retrieval of a consensus sequence for each path <inline-formula id="IEq475"><alternatives><tex-math id="M853">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
